name: Fantastic Four [PSX]
description:
Fantastic Four is an action game developed by Beenox, Beenox Studios and 7 Studios. It came out on 27-06-2005. Activision Blizzard published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Skip".
Fantastic Four is available on Xbox, Game Boy Advance, GameCube and PlayStation 2.
Rik Schaffer scored the game.
